<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I was sitting and medding one day and I was just about ready to ask for some buffs when I thought of an idea. Wouldn't it be easier for the classes that can actually do buffs know what each person in their group had on? All they would have to do is click on the persons name in their group and have a popup window show what buffs they have. I think that would make it easier on them and less aggrovating so they wouldn't have to hear "I need C2 please" over and over again. Buffs would just be a simple click away.
</FONT>
