<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
Groupmate should rarely have to ask for buffs.  Whoever is doing the buffing should cast the buff on themselves first and then on their groupmates.  That way when you see clarity,sow,symbol,etc blinking you know it is about to blink for everyone else.  On buffs that I do not cast on myself I try to keep it synced with one that I do so that I can keep track of those too.  When people see a buff always refreshed just after it starts blinking they are much more likely to remember you next time you are looking for a group.
</FONT>
<HR size="1" color="#dedfdf">
