Yeah, I used to use that little timer trick.  The only problem is when you reach higher levels.  Mana becomes VERY VERY precious and casting a buff on yourself when you don't need it is not a good idea.  Ecspecially when you are a Cleric.<P>You want my little idea on saving mana?  (I know you don't  hehe)<P>I would like to see a small change put into the game.  When you put your mouse pointer over somebody, a little bracket should appear around thier body.  And thier name should blink very brightly.  <P>When my tanks and the pulled mobs are all bunched up and beating the crap out of each other, sometimes I will cast a nuke or other spell on the wrong person.  Sometimes I see teammates casting nukes on the tanks in our group...   All because it's hard to see who your actually pointing at on the screen.<P>I think putting the brackets in would really help to solve the whole "Miss Cast" problem.<P>- Jaquio
