<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
I click on the person's name in the group box for buffs and heals. That targets them. Sometimes I use the f2-f6 buttons.<P>In a crowd, type /target (personsname). That also targets them. Their name will turn a different color when targetted, in case you need to actually walk up to them for some reason.<P>For mobs, either type /assist (tanksname) to get the mob, or if theres only 1 mob just hit f8.<P>This may or may not be on topic, just an information type thing.<P><BR>btw blah love yer sig  <IMG SRC="smile.gif" border="0"><P>--------------------<P>"Do as I say, not as I do" -someone or other
